---
const title = "未来";
---

<html lang="zh-CN">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>{title}</title>
    <style>
      :root {
        font-family: "Microsoft YaHei", "PingFang SC", "Noto Sans SC", sans-serif;
        color: #222;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f7fafc 0%, #e6f0ff 100%);
      }

      * {
        box-sizing: border-box;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }

      body {
        scroll-behavior: smooth;
        min-height: 100vh;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        padding: 24px;
      }

      .navbar {
        position: sticky;
        top: 0;
        z-index: 10;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
        padding: 18px 32px;
        background: rgba(255,255,255,0.75);
        backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      }

      .navbar nav a {
        margin-left: 20px;
        text-decoration: none;
        color: #334155;
      }

      .brand {
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #1f4fd1;
      }

      .page {
        width: 100%;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 32px;
        padding: 24px;
      }

      .card {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 760px;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);
        border-radius: 24px;
        padding: 48px;
        box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
        backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      }

      h1 {
        scroll-margin-top: 100px;
        font-size: 3rem;
        margin-bottom: 16px;
        color: #1f4fd1;
      }

      h2 {
        font-size: 2rem;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        color: #1e3a8a;
      }

      .post-list {
        display: grid;
        gap: 20px;
      }

      .post-item {
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 18px;
        background: #f8fbff;
        border: 1px solid #dbeafe;
      }

      .post-item h3 {
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        color: #1e40af;
      }

      p {
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        line-height: 1.8;
        color: #444;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }

      .btn {
        display: inline-block;
        margin-top: 12px;
        padding: 14px 28px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: #2563eb;
        color: white;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 600;
        transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
      }

      .btn:hover {
        transform: translateY(-2px);
        box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.3);
      }

      @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .card {
          padding: 28px;
        }

        h1 {
          font-size: 2.2rem;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <header class="navbar">
      <div class="brand">未来</div>
      <nav>
        <a href="#home">首页</a>
        <a href="#blog">博客</a>
        <a href="#about">关于</a>
      </nav>
    </header>

    <main class="page">
      <section class="card hero" id="home">
        <h1>你好，欢迎来到未来</h1>
        <p>
          “未来”是一个关于科技、思考与创造的个人空间。这里会记录我的灵感、项目、观察，以及对世界变化的想法。
        </p>
        <p>
          我希望把它做成一个像 Muzuki 风格一样简洁、安静、具有呼吸感的内容网站。
        </p>
        <a href="#blog" class="btn">阅读博客</a>
      </section>

      <section class="card posts" id="blog">
        <h2>最新文章</h2>
        <div class="post-list">
          <article class="post-item">
            <h3>AI 与人的协作边界</h3>
            <p>记录我对人工智能、创造力与未来社会关系的思考。</p>
          </article>
          <article class="post-item">
            <h3>我的 Astro 建站笔记</h3>
            <p>从零开始搭建个人网站的过程、踩坑和经验总结。</p>
          </article>
          <article class="post-item">
            <h3>关于“未来”的一些想法</h3>
            <p>为什么我想把这个网站命名为“未来”。</p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
